Package dev.nokee.platform.jni

Interface JniLibraryDependencies

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ComponentDependencies, JniLibraryNativeDependencies
    public interface JniLibraryDependencies
extends JniLibraryNativeDependencies, ComponentDependencies
    Allows the API and JVM implementation and native implementation dependencies of a JNI library to be specified. It also allows JVM runtime only as well as native link only and runtime only dependencies of a JNI library to be specified.
    Since:
    0.1

        action - The action to run to configure the dependency (project dependencies are ProjectDependency and external dependencies are ExternalModuleDependency).
